HEADWORD: Kummel
<hw>Kum"mel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[G.
<ets>k⟦uum⟧mmel</ets> cumin, caraway seed, L. <ets>cuminum</ets>. Cf.
<er>Cumin</er>.]</ety> <def>A Russian and German liqueur, consisting of
